name: SVGFEMorphologyElement
description: The SVGFEMorphologyElement interface corresponds to the <feMorphology> element.

members.name: SVGFEMorphologyElement.in1
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEMorphologyElement.operator
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the operator attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_MORPHOLOGY_OPERATOR_* constants defined on this interface.

members.name: SVGFEMorphologyElement.radiusX
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the X component of the radius attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEMorphologyElement.radiusY
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the Y component of the radius attribute of the given element.
